name: MyBusTimes
0: ”Alexa, ask My Bus Times when is the next bus?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my bus times
des: Brand new skill in its infancy that only works for the Chicago Transit Authority bus route 146 at the moment. As I learn how to develop more complex skills, I will add more features and functionality so that all Chicago public transit riders can use this! Stay tuned!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
